# {{ site.name }}

> {{ site.tagline }}

{{ site.name }} is a company-as-a-service platform delivered as a Claude Code plugin. It deploys {{ stats.agents }} AI agents across {{ stats.departments }} business departments — engineering, finance, marketing, legal, operations, product, sales, and support — plus {{ stats.skills }} workflow skills and {{ stats.commands }} commands. The platform compounds company knowledge over time: every problem solved becomes a pattern that accelerates future work.

{{ site.name }} is built for solo founders and small teams who want to operate at the scale of a full organization without hiring across every department.

## Use Cases

- **Feature Development:** Brainstorm requirements, create implementation plans, execute with parallel agents, run multi-agent code review, and compound learnings — all through a single `/soleur:go` command.
- **Business Validation:** Validate business ideas through structured market research, competitive analysis, and business model assessment using the business-validator agent.
- **Legal Document Generation:** Generate privacy policies, terms of service, GDPR policies, CLAs, and other legal documents through interactive workshops with the legal domain agents.
- **Marketing Strategy:** Run competitive intelligence scans, design pricing strategies, create content plans, and optimize conversion surfaces through the marketing domain's 11 specialist agents.
- **Financial Planning:** Build budgets, model P&L projections, track revenue, and generate investor-ready financial reports through the finance domain agents.
- **Operations Management:** Track expenses, research tools and providers, provision SaaS accounts, and optimize operational costs.

